The evidence with the title 'Warren Buffett: health care bill 'huge tax cut for guys like me ... ' says May 7, 2017  ... Berkshire Hathaway Inc chairman Warren Buffett fumed that healthcare costs are eating away at the U.S. economy like a " tapeworm " ... “ so it is a huge tax cut for guys like me , ” he said.  ... Buffett is a Democrat who vocally supported Hillary Clinton 's unsuccessful bid for the presidency against Trump . 
